{
  "stem": "27748.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was the American zone of occupation where my village lived-- existed, so I think her daughter seemed to have married an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Anyway, so that was the visit to Oberlauringen, my one-day visit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I-- after I left, I was totally torn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, on the one hand, there was Ernestine, but I also remembered the other lady, the coffee lady, and how I had the frozen smile on my face when I should have confronted them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the point of it all was I wasn't ready to confront, and so I wasn't available for healing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What they wanted, they wanted to be forgiven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was not able to forgive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I was also not confronting it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was only confronting it after I left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went-- I was increasingly uncomfortable in Israel, because of my problems, not because of the university or Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was my problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I arranged for a sabbatical to be at University of Toronto from 1976 to '77.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was really interested in finding a job back in America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, it so happened I didn't find a job while I was in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I stayed a second year in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eventually, I got a job near Baltimore, at the veterans hospital at Perry Point for heading a research center there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went-- we moved to Baltimore, but I failed to get a job in academics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I was there in the veterans hospital for three years and I failed in that job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I failed in the most important way for a researcher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I failed to get research grants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So eventually, the center was dissolved and I was left without work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'81.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then I was basically unemployed for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
